{"tid":2406950,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"情人節估計有大量處女膜破損","createTime":"2021-02-13T15:07:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-13T15:46:08.000Z","uid":89696,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bb2de7c7e4a4faa1ac7d35128bd0c5ddd2e13631","tid":2406950,"uid":89696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T15:07:41.000Z","msg":"「情人節、成人節」，一年一度情人節，例必為年青男女狂歡的日子。估計有大量處男處女將於今夜破處，當中不乏剛踏入合法做愛年齡的少年少女。有環保團體關注，超過數萬的安全套會被消耗而被沖入大海，對海洋生態造成嚴重破壞。有藥房東主表示，和往年一樣，預計聖15日清晨將會收到大量關於購買事後丸的查詢，強調事後丸須有醫生紙才可購買，「年年都走黎問，唔該知道自己呢晚有得扑嘢就買定袋啦」。最後有專家估計，飯後至淩晨時份，各大成人網站的瀏覽人次將到達高鋒，「唉，有著落就唔洗係屋企上網啦」。"},{"pid":"08bdc79f9f6f1e93c19e0f5e3fdb3ba1b5ec98ce","tid":2406950,"uid":56550,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T15:09:33.000Z","msg":"大量未到合法做愛年齡既少年少女都會做愛啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ab0c6b6a8b933b4e5eaeb933ff9e894d5f9d7f7","tid":2406950,"uid":391123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T15:46:08.000Z","msg":"估計?唔洗估啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n女神<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}